<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>TCFA 傑出店長應答練習室</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f4f6f1;
    --card: #fffdf7;
    --ink: #33413f;
    --muted: #6f7b78;
    --line: #dbe2dc;
    --brand: #647d78;
    --brand2: #8fa6a0;
    --accent: #e7eee9;
    --soft: #f0f4ed;
    --warn: #f2ead8;
    --good: #dfe9e2;
    --danger: #eadcdd;
    --clay: #b59376;
    --mauve: #8a9b94;
    --bluegray: #8ea1aa;
    --shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(54, 76, 72, .11);
    --radius: 18px;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Microsoft JhengHei", "Noto Sans TC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #e6eee9 0, #f4f6f1 42%, #fffdf7 100%);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  header {
    padding: 28px 18px 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5f7874, #9fb2a7);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr .7fr;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 42px);
    letter-spacing: .03em;
  }
  .subtitle {
    margin-top: 10px;
    max-width: 850px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .heroPanel {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.24);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  }
  .heroPanel b { font-size: 24px; display:block; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .heroStats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .stat {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px;
  }
  .stat .num {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .stat .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
  }
  main {
    padding: 20px 18px 60px;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 360px 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .card.pad { padding: 18px; }
  .sectionTitle {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--brand);
  }
  .field {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  select, textarea, input[type="text"] {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 11px 12px;
    background: #fffdf7;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 15px;
    outline: none;
  }
  select:focus, textarea:focus, input[type="text"]:focus {
    border-color: var(--brand2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(100,125,120,.16);
  }
  textarea {
    min-height: 220px;
    resize: vertical;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .btnRow {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  button {
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-weight: 800;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: #fff;
    background: var(--brand);
    transition: transform .05s ease, opacity .2s ease;
  }
  button:hover { opacity: .9; }
  button:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  button.secondary {
    background: #eaf0ea;
    color: var(--brand);
    border: 1px solid #d4ded7;
  }
  button.ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--brand);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  button.good {
    background: #78908a;
  }
  .notice {
    background: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid #d4ded7;
    color: #526762;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .small {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .questionHead {
    padding: 18px 20px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 5px 9px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--soft);
    color: #4f625e;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .tag.blue { background: #e6eeea; color: #566d68; }
  .tag.green { background: #e8ece5; color: #667866; }
  .tag.orange { background: #efe4d4; color: #7f684f; }
  .question {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 30px);
    line-height: 1.38;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: .01em;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .follow {
    background: #e7efea;
    border: 1px solid #d5e1da;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    color: #526b64;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .questionBody {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .twoCol {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .box {
    background: #fbfcf6;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 15px;
  }
  .box h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .dimGrid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .dim {
    background: #e9f0eb;
    color: #586f68;
    border: 1px solid #d9e4dd;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  ul {
    margin: 8px 0 0 20px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  li { margin: 4px 0; }
  .checklist {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .checkItem {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 22px 1fr;
    gap: 7px;
    align-items: center;
    background: #fffdf7;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 9px 10px;
    min-height: 42px;
  }
  .checkItem span {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .checkItem input {
    width: 17px;
    height: 17px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .compactDetails {
    margin-top: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #f8f5ed;
    padding: 9px 11px;
  }
  .compactDetails summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .compactDetails .checklist {
    margin-top: 9px;
  }
  .compactHint {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .hintPill {
    background: #fffdf7;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 9px 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .hintPill b { color: var(--brand); }
  .scoreWrap {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .scoreBar {
    flex: 1;
    background: #e5ebe6;
    border-radius: 999px;
    height: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .scoreFill {
    height: 100%;
    width: 0%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #647d78, #b59376);
    transition: width .2s;
  }
  .scoreText {
    min-width: 60px;
    text-align: right;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--brand);
  }
  .tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tab {
    background: #eef4ef;
    color: #4f625e;
    border: 1px solid #d9e4dd;
  }
  .tab.active {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--brand);
  }
  .pane { display: none; }
  .pane.active { display: block; }
  .footerNote {
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #fffaf0;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .listCompact {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .listCompact li {
    background: #fffdf7;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }
  .practiceMeta {
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    gap:10px;
    align-items:center;
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .empty {
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  button:disabled {
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: .48;
  }
  .lockedNotice {
    background: #fff7e8;
    border: 1px dashed #c8b79b;
    color: #6b5f4a;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .revealPanel {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffaf0, #e9f0eb);
    border: 1px solid #d9e4dd;
    color: #526762;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .reviewGrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(360px, .92fr);
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .reviewRight {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    align-self: start;
  }
  .answerSnapshot {
    min-height: 340px;
    max-height: 560px;
    overflow: auto;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    background: #fffdf7;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px;
    line-height: 1.72;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .answerEmpty {
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .checkGroupTitle {
    margin: 10px 0 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--brand);
  }
  .judgeLead {
    background: #fffdf7;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .judgeSub {
    margin-top: 10px;
    background: #f0f4ed;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px;
  }
  .judgePoints {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .judgePoint {
    background: #fffdf7;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }
  .judgePoint b {
    color: var(--brand);
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .reviewGrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .answerSnapshot { min-height: 260px; }
    .checklist { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .compactHint { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .heroStats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .twoCol { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media print {
    header, .filters, .btnRow, .tabs button, .footerNote { display: none !important; }
    body { background: #fffdf7; }
    .card { box-shadow: none; }
    main { padding: 0; }
  }
</style>

<link rel="manifest" href="manifest.webmanifest">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#647d78">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="TCFA應答練習室">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="icons/icon-192.png">
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="wrap hero">
    <div>
      <h1>TCFA 傑出店長應答練習室</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">
        課堂自學用：先完成自己的初稿，再用左右對照方式檢視回答面向、評審視角與補強資料，協助店長把真實經驗說清楚、說完整、說出管理價值。
      </div>
      <div class="heroStats">
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statTotal">78</div><div class="label">總題數</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statFast">20</div><div class="label">快問題</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statTopic">37</div><div class="label">主題分類</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statDone">0</div><div class="label">本機已完成題數</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="heroPanel">
      <b>課堂任務</b>
      每位店長至少完成 1 題：先獨立作答，再開啟後續檢視與補強。
      <div class="notice" style="margin-top:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.16);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);color:#fff;">
        本頁資料只儲存在自己的瀏覽器，不會自動上傳。
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="wrap grid">
    <aside class="card pad filters">
      <h2 class="sectionTitle">練習設定</h2>
      <div class="field">
        <label>練習模式</label>
        <select id="mode">
          <option value="all" selected>完整題庫 78 題｜建議課堂使用</option>
          <option value="fast">評審快問版 20 題｜快速練習</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>選題情境</label>
        <select id="scenario">
          <option value="">全部情境</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>主題分類</label>
        <select id="topic">
          <option value="">全部主題</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>使用優先度</label>
        <select id="priority">
          <option value="">全部</option>
          <option value="高">高</option>
          <option value="中高">中高</option>
          <option value="中">中</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="btnRow" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
        <button id="drawBtn">隨機抽題</button>
        <button class="secondary" id="prevBtn">上一題</button>
        <button class="secondary" id="nextBtn">下一題</button>
        <button class="secondary" id="resetBtn">清除條件</button>
      </div>

      <div class="notice">
        <b>建議使用方式</b><br>
        先花 3–5 分鐘寫初稿；送出初稿後，系統會呈現左右對照：左側保留剛剛的作答，右側上方勾選對應面向，右側下方提供評審視角。可依情境或主題練習；系統只會顯示目前條件下有題目的分類。
      </div>

      <div class="footerNote">
        <b>回答最低標準：</b><br>
        不能只說理念。至少要有一個具體案例、一個管理動作、一個成果證據，以及一句店長反思。
      </div>
    </aside>

    <section class="card" id="questionCard">
      <div class="empty">請先按「隨機抽題」，或調整左側條件後開始練習。</div>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>

<script>
